            <description><![CDATA[【转扩警惕！<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E6%96%B0%E5%9E%8B%E6%AF%92%E5%93%81%E4%BC%AA%E8%A3%85%E6%88%90%E9%82%AE%E7%A5%A8%E9%A5%BC%E5%B9%B2%23&amp;extparam=%23%E6%96%B0%E5%9E%8B%E6%AF%92%E5%93%81%E4%BC%AA%E8%A3%85%E6%88%90%E9%82%AE%E7%A5%A8%E9%A5%BC%E5%B9%B2%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#新型毒品伪装成邮票饼干#</span></a><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[怒]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_nu-0ddf642bed.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>】近日，海关检查进境邮件时，发现密封纸卡两张，藏有新型毒品LSD共计100片，俗称“邮票”，是一种强烈的半人工致幻剂。新型毒品善于伪装成各种模样，如“可乐”、“咔哇潮饮”、“干花”、“饼干”等。阿卫紧急提醒：警惕，远离毒品！<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B8%96%E5%91%8A%E8%AF%89%E4%BD%A0%E6%96%B0%E5%9E%8B%E6%AF%92%E5%93%81%E5%A4%9A%E8%83%BD%E8%A3%85%23&amp;extparam=%23%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B8%96%E5%91%8A%E8%AF%89%E4%BD%A0%E6%96%B0%E5%9E%8B%E6%AF%92%E5%93%81%E5%A4%9A%E8%83%BD%E8%A3%85%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#科普帖告诉你新型毒品多能装#</span></a>👇🏻（人民日报）<img style="" src="https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1he6w2afrumj20m81wvgtf.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1he6w2bl3p8j20u016nn25.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1he6w2c69mmj20u016nq89.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1he6w2cjagcj20u016ntdm.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax4.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1he6w29k7gwj20u016nn2u.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1he6w2deqjjj20u016n0xh.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br>]]></description>
